Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.80,0:22:14.64,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,总是不能如意
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:19.44,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,每天战战兢兢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:28.07,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,把自己的价值观强加于人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.07,0:22:31.12,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,-15)}又倍感痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.12,0:22:40.42,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,尽管如此 我们也要生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.63,0:22:46.67,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,就算受伤 就算流泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.01,0:22:51.93,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,明天也仍将到来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.34,0:22:57.52,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,不要哭泣 无论到哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.81,0:23:02.94,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,我们也会面对
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.36,0:23:05.94,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,-10)}想要做那个
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.94,0:23:12.57,Ending Theme - CN,,0,0,0,,怀抱着希望有意义的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.00,0:01:55.01,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(980,750)\fs80}第7话 「弹弹软软的」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.99,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an1\p1\c&H2D2D2D&\1a&H32&\3c&H8C8C8C&\bord1.5\pos(1315,625)}m 0 0 l 490 0 l 490 260 l 0 260
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:18.99,Text,,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\fs32\pos(1330,385)}魔力是魔女所拥有的魔法的力量\N魔压则是为了让魔力流动起来 \N两者的关系就像储存的水和济水的泵\N如果没法正常控制魔压\N魔力将一下子全部放出 立刻用完\N相反则是储存了过多魔力 \N但完全无法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:13.82,Explain,,0,0,0,,泰尔斯海灵岛：属荷兰 西弗里西亚群岛之一
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.22,0:23:39.18,Explain,,0,0,0,,鬼雾：2005年上映的美国恐怖电影 讲述一个在海边小镇上 镇民举办庆祝活动\N一股怪雾突如其来 随后发生恐怖事件的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.11,0:00:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,异形出现 全队出击
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,目标高度15000英尺 速度350节
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.74,0:00:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,正在朝本基地前进
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,预计于60秒后在泰尔斯海灵岛上空接敌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.37,0:00:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:02:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉 我的魔力 还没有完全恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事 你前段时间不是能正常控制魔压了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.47,0:02:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,前几天在汉堡的作战不是也能正常飞行了么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.61,0:02:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 听军医说 魔力和魔压是两回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.12,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,把容器中储存的水当成是魔力的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,魔压就是从中适量取出水的水泵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.19,0:02:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这一块确实已经能正常控制了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.29,0:02:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 现在的芳佳 注入魔力的“水管”仍未恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 一旦将魔力全部用完后
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,要完全回复需要很长时间
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此 这么一来即使能正常控制
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有关键的魔力 仍然不能飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,说不定是前些天的战斗让她用力过猛了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说的话根本原因还是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.94,0:02:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,不是你们的错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.57,0:03:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 宫藤为了回复魔力需要休养
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.41,0:03:06.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大家请这件事放在心上 明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.26,0:03:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这个药草也不对
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,对魔力回复没什么帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,进森林之前先找佩琳商量下就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.90,0:03:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等着我 芳佳 我肯定会找到带回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.42,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.30,0:03:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你就带回来了是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.63,0:03:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个不知道是啥的壶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.84,0:04:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 总觉得很奇特 有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都看不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.93,0:04:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想看 想看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是很旧的东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.93,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,莉涅没受伤真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不能一个人乱来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.51,0:04:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,抱… 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.06,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你有资格说别人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有机可乘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.08,0:04:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.32,0:04:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这… 这是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:32.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是土偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.62,Default,,0,0,0,,土偶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,快看快看 胸比佩琳的还大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,多管闲事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.42,0:04:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,来来 还不快对这个胸部下拜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.76,0:04:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你差不多…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁奇尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.81,0:04:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 鲁奇尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁奇尼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.78,0:05:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.95,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁奇尼少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,胸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.21,0:05:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,摇起来了 摇起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.09,0:05:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.47,0:05:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好痒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.59,0:05:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你 你 你在干什么 宫藤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,身体自己动起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.80,0:05:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静点 服部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这是常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.77,0:05:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.28,0:05:42.11,Default,,0,0,0,,耳朵和尾巴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说 魔力回复了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.69,0:05:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你这么问我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说 是因为摸了鲁奇尼变大的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.95,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.16,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.63,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,土偶它
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,浮起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嘻嘻 献给你 丰收的祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,嘻嘻？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,丰收的祈愿？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.31,0:06:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,跳起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,想要 丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.52,0:06:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.77,0:06:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,静夏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,迷失自我了吗 鲁奇尼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.83,0:06:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.57,0:06:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,情况不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.32,0:06:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快追
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,快看 艾拉 都开的很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,这些家伙真让人羡慕 竟能得到萨妮娅的照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 萨妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.94,0:06:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:07:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不够 果实 完全不够
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,给予你 祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.32,0:07:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,鲁奇尼 你这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.87,0:07:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.79,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙 快放开萨妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,萨妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.50,0:07:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 你差不多够了 鲁奇尼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.04,0:07:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,萨妮娅 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.84,0:07:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉 我的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,很难受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,「变成这样了」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,连萨妮娅都
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.85,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,925)}「艾拉也觉得大点好吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,和胸部大小无关 我喜欢萨妮娅本来的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.03,0:07:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉她能听懂萨妮娅在说什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.49,0:07:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,真怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,925)}「艾拉」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.49,0:07:51.69,Default,,0,0,0,,萨妮娅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.29,0:08:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,连艾拉都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.67,0:08:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.17,0:08:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,成熟的魔女 还差6个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.71,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,「祈愿丰收」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,「献给巫女」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.21,0:08:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,叶格大尉 我们该怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,就算你这么问我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然只是我的推测
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.15,0:08:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,第一 鲁奇尼大概是被那个土偶诅咒才袭胸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.99,0:08:27.15,Default,,0,0,0,,诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,第二 被诅咒的人通过袭胸让对方的胸变大 同时扩散诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,确实 桑尼亚她们胸变大之后就像变了个人似的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.12,0:08:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,然后第三 诅咒的目的是为了凑齐9个成熟的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.87,0:08:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,9人 就是说还会有6个牺牲者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 这都是我的责任 是我把土偶带来的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,莉涅
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.73,0:08:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,莉涅你没有错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.35,0:09:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.44,0:09:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 如果是因为诅咒 那该怎么办才好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我想 只要破坏那个土偶就能解开诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,各位 请助我一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,第一目标是土偶 一找到就将它破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.21,0:09:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉和桑尼亚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.91,0:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她们也会扩散诅咒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过元凶是土偶的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.56,0:09:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,将诅咒从根源斩断 就是这么回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.48,0:09:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,把鲁奇尼还给我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.90,0:09:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也把祈愿 给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,哼 不需要 就算没有诅咒 我的果实也够丰收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,最近好像有点下垂了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,下垂胸夏莉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.38,0:10:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,下垂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,叶格大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.72,0:10:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.43,0:10:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 连夏莉都
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤 我们先撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.06,0:10:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,那已经不是叶格大尉了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,明明必须要破坏土偶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在被抓到的话 我们也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.25,0:10:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,莉涅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.08,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,别管我 快跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.16,0:10:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,925)}「让果实丰收吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.87,0:10:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,925)}「让我揉胸吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,这么下去的话 莉涅她也会…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,又变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.72,0:11:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,真羡慕佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.72,0:11:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶 胸大就这么得意吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.31,0:11:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,莉涅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.66,0:11:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛斯特曼中尉 你没受伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.99,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 只是慌乱了一下而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.66,0:11:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 连夏莉都
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.66,0:11:27.91,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 土偶的硬度超乎寻常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,用平底锅敲上去完全无效
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.42,0:11:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要更可靠的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,佩琳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 说起来有个不错的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.85,0:11:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,之前藏在那个箱子里了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.35,0:11:44.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在土豆里面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.81,0:11:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是佩琳 准备得真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看 在哪儿呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.35,0:11:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,克洛斯特曼中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.69,0:11:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.40,0:11:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,「你们在干什么呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.40,0:11:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,佩琳 你的胸
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.44,0:12:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,「在摇！」「在摇动呀！」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.08,0:12:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快逃吧 中尉已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.12,0:12:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,服部
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.54,0:12:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,静夏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.72,0:12:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧 芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.52,0:12:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我能做的只是争取时间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.73,0:12:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,静夏 怎么办啊 诅咒扩散的更大了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,给土地以丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,为巫女献上身体
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,特露德 我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,已经到晚餐时间了 今天是谁做菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.73,0:13:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,明娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.06,0:13:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么穿成这副模样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这样会感冒的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了 明娜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了你们… 搞什么玩意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.57,0:13:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,这情况不对劲 因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,桑妮亚和佩林的胸部变得比我还大了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.17,0:13:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,她们一直都比你大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.97,0:13:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,但是情况确实不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,哈特曼 你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.47,0:13:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,这次轮到我来救特露德了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,哈特曼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.24,0:14:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你到底想干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.18,0:14:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去司令室求援吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.15,0:14:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不会吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.04,0:15:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,巫女  献上祈祷 魔女 都要丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我跑不动了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,宫藤 莉涅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克霍隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.60,0:15:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,少校 是土偶 快打坏那个土偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,那个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会 连巴克霍隆的巨力都没有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.78,0:15:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.16,0:15:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那明娜她们也都被诅咒了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,总之 现在要紧的事是先平息事态
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.17,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我会飞到海牙基地请求救援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你躲到安全的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.42,0:15:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,清楚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克霍隆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:49.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不用担心 我一定会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.27,0:15:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 发动机打不着
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,「我没准许出击哦 特露德」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,明娜 难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.15,0:16:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,925)}「这是什么?」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.57,0:16:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行脚的火花塞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住她
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 等 等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.83,0:16:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,丰收的魔女集齐了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,为巫女献上丰收的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,利涅 刚刚那个尖叫声…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.43,0:16:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,巴克霍隆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那只剩下我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.90,0:16:42.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那个诅咒是像传染病一样的的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.32,0:16:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是病的话 我只要恢复魔力就能治好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.91,0:16:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来想帮助芳佳 结果却让她更痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.87,0:16:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.66,0:16:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我有件事拜托你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.67,0:17:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让我摸摸你的胸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,白天我摸过鲁基尼的胸后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,魔力不是恢复了一小会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.66,0:17:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以再来一次的话 可能就又恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好羞耻
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,但这都是我的错…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.89,0:17:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,而且看着芳佳这认真的眼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.44,0:17:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我拒绝不了…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.53,0:17:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,就一下下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.37,0:17:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.53,0:17:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,利涅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.30,0:17:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为巫女献上丰收的祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,对啊 已经有九个人了 不需要我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.53,0:18:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在只剩下我了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,被诅咒的鲁奇尼 说要向巫女献上祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以芳佳是安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我会保护芳佳的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,大家醒过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,丰收的魔女 向巫女献上祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.86,0:18:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,给这片土地带来丰收…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.39,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳 趁现在跑起来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,利涅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.23,0:19:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,干扰仪式 不可原谅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.65,0:19:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.74,0:19:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳  你的魔力！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.97,0:19:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.30,0:20:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部太可怕了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.55,0:20:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抓到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.37,0:20:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳 胸部没什么可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.38,0:20:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,根据调查
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这个土偶似乎是很久以前的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,为了祈求丰收的仪式而制作的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.35,0:20:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,丰胸？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不对 是丰收
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.09,0:20:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,仪式需要九位魔女和一位巫女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们被选中了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,但是为什么巫女会是宫藤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.02,0:20:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,桑妮亚更清纯更适合当巫女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.98,0:20:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别说了啦 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是因为宫藤打破了罐子的封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.65,0:21:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 它可能觉得封印被解除了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.91,0:21:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易变大的胸就…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,让胸部变大这种好事… 不 恶趣味有什么好的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是过去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.08,0:21:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}让胸部变大 再来一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.84,0:21:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,丰满的胸部象征着丰收吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.72,0:21:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,胸部是丰收的象征…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.30,0:21:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,所以宫藤的魔力才会瞬间恢复吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,不 她只是摸到了胸部 兴奋起来了而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是宫藤的作风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.23,0:21:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.36,0:21:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那你再摸一下别人的胸部试试看？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.86,0:21:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,芳佳？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,利涅 那时我没有摸到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.70,0:21:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,现在补摸一下可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,不… 不可以！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.55,0:23:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,桑妮亚 马上就到萨图努斯祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.72,0:23:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今年还要穿那件红色的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.06,0:23:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你看起来很高兴呢 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.68,0:23:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,因为是和你一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 强袭魔女  「鬼雾」
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,诶 什么鬼雾？
